text: Riverton High School is a high school in Riverton, Wyoming and forms part of the Fremont County School District Number 25. In 2017, it had an enrollment of 787 students and a faculty of 46 teachers in grades 9-12. In 2018, it had an enrollment of 766 students and a faculty of 47 teachers in grades 9-12. ==References== * Category:Educational institutions with year of establishment missing Category:Public high schools in Wyoming Category:Schools in Fremont County, Wyoming Category:Riverton, Wyoming
